&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Serve as the &lt;strong&gt;RevOps point of contact&lt;/strong&gt; for mid-level managers in Sales, Marketing, and Customer Success to define requirements and deliver solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead complex, cross-functional projects&lt;/strong&gt; (e.g., territory planning, sales compensation design, new product launches) from scope definition through implementation and post-launch analysis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Data, Reporting, and Forecasting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oversee the data governance framework&lt;/strong&gt; to ensure high data quality, accuracy, and consistency across all revenue systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the annual revenue model&lt;/strong&gt; using available resources to ensure the accuracy of the model.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Work with leadership to &lt;strong&gt;develop and maintain standardized, executive-level reporting and dashboards&lt;/strong&gt; that provide actionable insights into pipeline health, forecasting accuracy, and GTM performance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contribute to the weekly and quarterly revenue forecasting process&lt;/strong&gt; by providing data-backed analysis and flagging potential risks or opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
