&lt;p&gt;As an Site Reliability Engineering (SRE) Manager, you will&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience of managing and growing high performing engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have experience with Kubernetes and Terraform&lt;/

